dict.string:
query=$(/usr/bin/base64 <<< "$1") OPTS="--RegionId=${region}" OPTS="$OPTS --InstanceId.1=${vmId}" OPTS="$OPTS --Name=cmd-${vmId}" OPTS="$OPTS --Type=${cmdType}" OPTS="$OPTS --CommandContent=$query" OPTS="$OPTS --ContentEncoding=Base64"
aliyun ecs RunCommand $OPTS | jq -r .InvokeId

[{"title":"Pods (all)","arg":"\/api\/v1\/pods","subtitle":"describe pods --all-namespaces"},{"title":"Pods (default)","arg":"\/api\/v1\/namespaces\/default\/pods","subtitle":"describe pods --n=default"},{"title":"DaemonSet (all)","arg":"\/apis\/apps\/v1\/daemonsets","subtitle":"describe daemonset --all-namespace"},{"title":"DaemonSet (default)","arg":"\/apis\/apps\/v1\/namespace\/default\/daemonsets","subtitle":"describe daemonset -n=default"},{"title":"Services (all)","arg":"\/api\/v1\/services","subtitle":"describe services --all-namespaces"},{"title":"Services (default)","arg":"\/api\/v1\/namespaces\/default\/services","subtitle":"describe services --n=default"},{"title":"Namespaces","arg":"\/api\/v1\/namespaces","subtitle":"describe namespaces"},{"title":"Console","arg":"console","subtitle":"Open cluster console"}]

mkdir -p $HOME/.kube/${cluster}
if ! [ -f $HOME/.kube/${cluster}/config ]; then aliyun cs DescribeClusterV2UserKubeconfig --ClusterId=${cluster} | jq -r .config > $HOME/.kube/${cluster}/config fi
if ! [ -f $HOME/.kube/${cluster}/server.host ]; then cat $HOME/.kube/${cluster}/config | grep "server:" | xargs | cut -d' ' -f2 | xargs > $HOME/.kube/${cluster}/server.host fi
if ! [ -f $HOME/.kube/${cluster}/server.cert ]; then cat $HOME/.kube/${cluster}/config | grep certificate-authority-data | cut -d':' -f2 | xargs | base64 -d > $HOME/.kube/${cluster}/server.cert fi
if ! [ -f $HOME/.kube/${cluster}/client.cert ]; then cat $HOME/.kube/${cluster}/config | grep client-certificate-data | cut -d':' -f2 | xargs | base64 -d > $HOME/.kube/${cluster}/client.cert fi
if ! [ -f $HOME/.kube/${cluster}/client.key ]; then cat $HOME/.kube/${cluster}/config | grep client-key-data | cut -d':' -f2 | xargs | base64 -d > $HOME/.kube/${cluster}/client.key fi
